'''泛甲殼動物'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|Pancrustacea}}）是[[甲殼類|甲殼類]]及[[六足亞門|六足亞門]]的總稱<ref>{{cite journal |first1=J. |last1=Zrzavý |first2=P. |last2=Štys|title=The basic body plan of arthropods: insights from evolutionary morphology and developmental biology|journal=''[[Journal_of_Evolutionary_Biology|Journal of Evolutionary Biology]]'' |year=1997|volume=10|pages=353–67|doi=10.1007/s000360050029|language=en}}</ref>。這個分類與[[缺角類|缺角類]]有矛盾，因缺角類只包含[[多足綱|多足綱]]及[[六足亞門|六足亞門]]，並認為甲殼類是較為疏遠的。截至2010年，泛甲殼動物已被廣泛接受<ref>{{cite journal|author=Omar Rota-Stabelli, Ehsan Kayal, Dianne Gleeson, Jennifer Daub, Jeffrey L. Boore, Maximilian J. Telford, Davide Pisani, Mark Blaxter & Dennis V. Lavrov|year=2010|title=Ecdysozoan mitogenomics: evidence for a common origin of the legged invertebrates, the Panarthropoda|journal=Genome Biology and Evolution|volume=2|pages=425–40|doi=10.1093/gbe/evq030|pmid=20624745|url=http://gbe.oxfordjournals.org/content/2/425|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120710135634/http://gbe.oxfordjournals.org/content/2/425|archivedate=2012-07-10}}</ref>。

多項[[分子|分子]]研究都支持泛甲殼動物是[[單系群|單系群]]<ref>{{cite journal|author=Jeffrey W. Shultz & Jerome C. Regier|title=Phylogenetic analysis of arthropods using two nuclear protein-encoding genes supports a crustacean + hexapod clade|journal=Proceedings of the Royal Society B|volume=267|pages=1011–9|url=http://www.life.umd.edu/entm/shultzlab/opiliomd/papers/ProcRSocLondB.pdf|doi=10.1098/rspb.2000.1104|year=2000|pmid=10874751|issue=1447|access-date=2010-09-17|archive-date=2017-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808085714/http://www.life.umd.edu/entm/shultzlab/opiliomd/papers/ProcRSocLondB.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=A review of arthropod phylogeny: new data based on ribosomal DNA sequences and direct character optimization|author=Gonzalo Giribet & Carles Ribera|journal=Cladistics|volume=16|pages=204-31|year=2000|doi=10.1111/j.1096-0031.2000.tb00353.x}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |url=https://science.sciencemag.org/content/299/5614/1887 |first1=Francesco |last1=Nardi |first2=Giacomo |last2=Spinsanti |first3=Jeffrey L. |last3=Boore |first4=Antonio |last4=Carapelli |first5=Romano |last5=Dallai |first6=Francesco |last6=Frati |title=Hexapod Origins: Monophyletic or Paraphyletic? |journal=[[科学_(期刊)|Science (journal)]] |volume=299 |issue=5614 |pages=1887-9 |year=2003 |doi=DOI: 10.1126/science.1078607 |pmid=12649480 |access-date=2019-12-27 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225094420/https://science.sciencemag.org/content/299/5614/1887 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|author=Jerome C. Regier ''et al.''|year=2010|title=Arthropod relationships revealed by phylogenomic analysis of nuclear protein-coding sequences|journal=Nature|volume=463|pages=1079–83|doi=10.1038/nature08742|pmid=20147900|issue=7284}}</ref>，但大部份甲殼類都是[[昆蟲|昆蟲]]的[[並系群|並系群]]，即昆蟲是[[演化|演化]]自甲殼類祖先。

==分类==
泛甲殼動物由原來的[[顎足綱|顎足綱]]分拆，再與同屬[[甲殻亞門|甲殻亞門]]的[[介形綱|介形綱]]及[[軟甲綱|軟甲綱]]重新組合，成為[[寡甲總綱|寡甲總綱]]（[[Oligostraca|Oligostraca]]）和[[多甲總綱|多甲總綱]] （[[Multicrustacea|Multicrustacea]]）兩個[[總綱|總綱]]{{r|WoRMS_1066}}。{{as of|2019|12|27}}，[[WoRMS|WoRMS]]紀錄泛甲殼動物包括下列各分類單元{{r|WoRMS_1066}}：
* [[甲殼亞門|甲殼亞門]] Crustacea
** [[鰓足綱|鰓足綱]] Branchiopoda：原為演化支 Vericrustacea之下的分類單元；
** [[頭蝦綱|頭蝦綱]] Cephalocarida
** [[多甲總綱|多甲總綱]] Multicrustacea{{r|WoRMS_845959|Regier et al 2010}}
*** [[六幼生綱|六幼生綱]] Hexanauplia{{r|WoRMS_889925}}
**** [[橈足類|橈足亞綱]] Copepoda：原為演化支 [[Vericrustacea|Vericrustacea]]之下的綱級分類單元；
**** [[微虾亚纲|微虾亚纲]] Tantulocarida：原為演化支 Vericrustacea之下的綱級分類單元；
**** [[鞘甲亚纲|鞘甲亚纲]] Thecostraca：原為演化支 Vericrustacea之下的綱級分類單元；
*** [[软甲纲|软甲纲]] Malacostraca：原為演化支 Vericrustacea之下的分類單元；
** [[寡甲總綱|寡甲總綱]] Oligostraca{{r|WoRMS_845957|Zrzavý et al 1997}}
*** [[魚介形綱|魚介形綱]] Ichthyostraca{{r|WoRMS_845958}}
**** [[鰓尾亞綱|鰓尾亞綱]] Branchiura：原為綱級
**** [[舌形動物類|舌形亞綱]] Pentastomida：原為綱級，又名[[五口纲|五口纲]]
